// lexicon takes the same token description format [...] as grammar formalism  except that the  brackets are ommitted [... ] 
// and the single quotation marks for 'stem' are omitted  
// Of course the lexical lookup uses different procedure  instead of full FSA compiling for efficiency consideration.  
// stem: f1 f2  == ['stem':f1 f2] // after colon  it is mainly feature assignment
// if we want STEM and POS together to be condition  use the format: stem v: ... == [stem v:...]

// 字典 1-character glossary
败: defeated buyuW nW buyW freeM minusEvent c1clear defeat V 				// suspend badW for now as it is used as "buy" in social media: needs special treatment in rules  removed features: damage decline
饱: plusEvent DEbuyuW freeM valueUp c1clear enjoy beFull perF A 				// suspend buyuW  as it is too specific when used as buyu
饱饱: plusEvent up DEbuyuW valueUp enjoy beFull perF A 饱				// up  especially for food

由于: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
只要: V0 NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW vNPVB TO
不但: NOTaspectW butW NOTobjectW TO
不管: V0 NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW RB 
不论: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW RB 
不光: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
否则: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
即使: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
既然: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
尽管: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
可是: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
另外: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
其次: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
然而: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
无论: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW RB 
因此: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
于是: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW RB				// RB instead of TO on purpose because it can be inserted between S and Pred.
不然: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
除非: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
此外: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
从而: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
何况: NOTaspectW butW NOTobjectW TO
假如: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO 如果
接着: goOn NOTaspectW butW catchF sRB NOTobjectW TO
哪怕: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
哪怕是: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO 即使
要不: NOTaspectW butW NOTobjectW TO
要不就: NOTaspectW butW complexM NOTobjectW TO
要是: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
因而: NOTaspectW sconjW sRB NOTobjectW TO
而且: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
与其: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
然后: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
因为: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO				// it can be used both as prep and sconjW
// 是因为: NOTaspectW sconjW xC leftB NOTobjectW TO 因为				// leftB: used more often to link to preceding S
所以: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
如果: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
虽然: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
但是: NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO
即便: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
假若: NOTaspectW sconjW NOTobjectW TO
不过: precdW NOTaspectW butW sRB NOTobjectW TO				// = but
